latestIgtvVideos.caption:
So this is what happened in Bangalore’s first ever makeup masterclass by an Indian artist- had to be by Manjeet Khehra  ofcourse 😜 in March 2019. 
Three looks were taught in detail. With detailed product knowledge both affordable and luxury brands. Lots of tips and tricks of makeup, social media and my personal experiences were shared. Our goodie bag value finally crossed more than our ticket prices. What an extraordinary class it was 😍😍

latestIgtvVideos.title: This is how I Sketched myself
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Here’s a quick tutorial on how I sketched myself. Just use any white face paint or foundation, set it with a white setting powder or talcum powder like I did. And outline all your features and wrinkles with a liner/kajal. That’s it. A simple three step, three product yet fancy look 😍😍

latestIgtvVideos.caption:
